# 🎓 Certix - Certificate Generation & Email Automation

## 📌 Overview
Certix is a Flask-based web application that automates certificate generation and email delivery. It reads participant details from Google Sheets, generates personalized PDF certificates, and emails them automatically.

## ✨ Features
- Generate personalized certificates
- Read participant data from Google Sheets
- Automatic email sending
- PDF certificate generation
- Flask Web Interface
- Bulk certificate processing

## 🛠 Technologies Used
- Python
- Flask
- Google Sheets API
- ReportLab
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript

## 📂 Project Structure

```
app.py
templates/
static/
utils/
requirements.txt
```

## 🚀 Installation

```bash
git clone https://github.com/uniquehp19-cb/Certix.git
cd Certix

pip install -r requirements.txt

python app.py
```


## 🔮 Future Enhancements

- User Authentication
- Certificate Templates
- QR Code Verification
